cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.DS, cs.CE 

This paper deals with expert systems based on causal probabilistic networks, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses data structuring techniques, which are relevant to computer engineering (cs.CE) and data structures (cs.DS). The topic of approximations in Bayesian belief networks is also related to statistical inference (cs.SI).
